Texts.Eng: A statue dedicated to Benjamin "Meuterion" Deust.
Texts.Por: Uma estátua dedicada a Benjamin "Meuterion" Deust.

Texts.Eng: It is said that statues to great men are made of the stones thrown at them in their lifetime.
Texts.Por: Diz-se que estátuas para grandes homens são feitas das pedras jogadas neles em sua vida.

Texts.Eng: The plaque claims this is dedicated to the grand Benjamin "Meuterion" Deust.
The plaque reads "A statue dedicated to Benjamin "Meuterion" Deust."
